        "text": "6–11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Convinced that God will manifest His authority, the Psalmist sees the machinations of his enemies turning to their own defeat, and utters resolutions of joyous thanksgiving.",
        "children": []
      },
